===Overview===
'''The Aquabats''' were a superhero musical group from Earth, of which [[Peter Quill (Earth-616)|Peter Quill]] and [[Lydia (Earth-616)|Lydia]] were fans. Together, they sang the band's song "[[Wikipedia:Super Rad!|Super Rad!]]" along with [[Tiberius (Earth-616)|Tiberius]] onboard the [[Bad Boy]] as they escaped a Badoon prison ship.{{r|Legendary Star-Lord Vol 1 3}}
